channel.title: Working Class7.java for Bluurrs?
channel.description: I've noticed most, if not all bluurrs clients do not come with a working class7.java. The .class file works fine, however, when I decompile it, it throws loads of errors. If I remove the file, and compiler normally, it shows no errors. If this doesn't make sense, I'll try explaining it again.
